text: Rachel Alexandra Mercaldo (born March 4, 1977, in Staten Island, New York), known professionally as Rockell, is an American freestyle, hi-NRG and pop singer-songwriter, best known for her 1997 hit single, "In a Dream". She is Puerto Rican. Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:American singer-songwriters Category:Singers from New York City
